      • guessCsvRA

        public static CSVRandomAccess guessCsvRA(File f,
                                         int guessLines,
                                         boolean hasHeader)
                                  throws FileNotFoundException,
                                         IOException
        Opens a csv-parser for the given file and tries to predict the quote character and the field-delimiter based on the first number of lines.
        After it reads the first lines it will reopen the file with a configured csv-parser.
        This means, that the file must be re-readable e.g no pipe
        Parameters:
        f - the file to open
        guessLines - how many lines to read in for guessing the parameters
        Returns:
        a CavParser for the file
        Throws:
        FileNotFoundException
        IOException
